Package: Icare
Title: Integrated Clinical Analysis and Risk Evaluation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("John", "Doe", email = "john.doe@example.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: 
    Provides tools for clinical data preprocessing, survival analysis, 
    and machine learning model development. Includes specialized functions for 
    handling missing data, outlier detection, and risk stratification.
